{"tid":609802,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)左膠迷宮3 無頭谷 老豆又出動","createTime":"2018-03-29T10:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T16:50:01.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa53c372eef362a01e3311f884dc3bdba29a94a","tid":609802,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6lkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=dc648a1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6lkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=4a5bc782\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/24/Maze_Runner_The_Death_Cure_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F24%2FMaze_Runner_The_Death_Cure_Poster.jpg&h=db67ddd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fd/Sleepy_hollow_1999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffd%2FSleepy_hollow_1999.jpg&h=6fed56a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/da/The_Commuter_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fda%2FThe_Commuter_Poster.jpg&h=371d8353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.接續上集，湯瑪士等人透過8個月的漫長計畫找到民豪被押送的裝甲列車，透過巧妙戰術劫走車廂救出數十名免疫者，然而民豪卻因突然換位而不在該車廂繼續被押往末日之都，等回到海港邊秘密基地的眾人發現時已經太晚，此時分成兩派，一派主張前往末日之都救人，一派主張放棄，因為改裝中的貨船希望號已經完工眾人可以直接出海永遠擺脫WCKD<br />\n<br />\n2.電影背景設定為1799年的紐約市，主張以科學方式辦案的警察伊卡波&middot;克瑞恩常與守舊的上司發生衝突，上司為了擺脫他便派遣他到鄉下一個名叫「沉睡谷」的小鎮調查一連串神秘命案，凡&middot;蓋瑞特等三名死者皆被斬首。當伊卡波抵達沉睡谷後，便直接進入鎮上首富巴爾圖斯&middot;凡&middot;塔賽爾的家中，在宴會上他無意被凡&middot;塔賽爾的女兒卡翠娜吻了一下，從此兩人間便萌發了愛情，而招來卡翠娜男友布朗&middot;凡&middot;布魯恩特的忌妒和不滿<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述麥可&middot;麥考利是一位保險推銷員，每日會搭乘通勤列車前往芝加哥的公司；某日，在麥克被開除後，一名神秘的陌生女人與他聯繫，對方表示如果麥可能在到達Cold Spring車站前發現一名「不屬於這裡」的乘客並安裝定位裝置，那他就可以拿走10萬美元。麥可在解決該事件時，意識到自己陷入了一個龐大的犯罪陰謀之中；他和家人，所有前往終點站的乘客的生命都處於危險，只有他才能揭開背後隱藏的秘密<br />\n<br />\n8 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6lkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=39b5c717\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6lkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=8f8cbdaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a716e020b5ef4b50f69627e4312b7a7daffdc2","tid":609802,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe607f884c04a21f1ea992492e9fced93ed62c68","tid":609802,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"